        "client_msg_id": "0DC7F34F-0BA8-495E-A83A-4D0791D21A59",
        "text": "We need to separate the human interface from the machine representation. I’m perfectly happy with a text or binary machine representation. But for the human interface, there are many things for which it is impossible to map them cleanly into text. You could use text to _describe_ them, but that would be lossy.",
